These Yorkshire puddings are designed to rise tall and light with a crisp shell and a lightly
chewy center. You want to take more control over how the puddings come out? Read up
on the science of Yorkshire puddings (https://www.seriouseats.com/2015/12/food-lab-yorkshire-
pudding-popover-best-method-science.html) to learn about the Ąner points of the process.
